<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437942>
    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Collected specimens. Gerromorpha, Veliidae. A. Rhagovelia modesta, apterous male from Casimiro de Abreu / Silva Jardim, Rio de Janeiro (−22.4342, −42.2934). B. Rhagovelia pseudotijuca, apterous male from São José do Barreiro, São Paulo (−22.7349, −44.6162). C, D. Rhagovelia rioana from Angra dos Reis, Rio de Janeiro (−23.1414, −44.2987). C. Apterous male. D. Apterous female. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437942/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437946>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas. A. Rhagovelia modesta. B. Rhagovelia pseudotijuca. C. Rhagovelia rioana. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records." ;
